Naming conventions of vamps S-Lang functions and variables
-------------------------------------------------------------

_*_	- read only status variable

v_*	- Vamps variable or function only available (or making sense) 
	  during a run

m_*	- Matrix operations

v_i_*	- Vamps interactive scripts

f_* 	- Output/input file variable manipulation 

g_* 	- Low level graphics
	  (should be independent on graphics library used

*_plot	- Simple high level plotting routines
	  (should be independent on graphics library used

pl_*	- GNU lib-plot interface routines

ag_*	- agl graphics library routines

*	- the rest
